About Brooke

Newly married and living in my home town of Geelong.

Enjoy sharing my experience and knowledge with others.

Almost 5 years working full-time in an Multisystem Therapy - Psychiatric (MST-P) program in Victoria. Supervision experience.

Wish to develop my teaching skills to support my future lecturing aspirations.
